As D.I.S.C. is massive, it should be enjoyed as a good red wine... take
a sip now and then. Read a few articles now, and some later on. You'll
never know when the next issue appears. For us to be able to come up with
a great issue, the «c2»demo scene «c5»got to be active. To have an entire mag
filled with the usual editors about editors articles are boring. So we
depend on all of you out there to produce some «c2»great demos, intros,
slideshows, musicdisks in addition to mags. «c5»This year has begun with new
optimism as Amiga has launched their «c2»Amiga OS 3.9 «c5»late last year, and the
new «c2»AmigaOne «c5»card will soon arrive. And a few good productions have already
